{"tid":407153,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"遊戲截圖就是我們的回憶 黎分享過去行過咩路","createTime":"2017-09-20T08:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T04:24:15.000Z","uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e6c3bfe59058a3769147dabebe78d82eacc47aa1","tid":407153,"uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:41:04.000Z","msg":"玩ONLINE GAME成日都影下唔同野<br />\n通常保留到都會保留 中毒先冇計要洗機冇晒D相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入黎分享下大家過去嘅遊戲相<br />\n話唔定可以起度相認<br />\n<br />\n多仇口就記得唔好出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪已經冇人玩ONLINE GAME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">毒撚開POST冇人理</span></span>"},{"pid":"201d7067605f60e18a80964951ef6df36e039b82","tid":407153,"uid":9767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:07:01.000Z","msg":"超時空戰記真係好好玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e34589e9720ea549a2b44a43958f2d3b418bb7","tid":407153,"uid":48776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:20:55.000Z","msg":"玩過n隻主要係升lv既olg<br />\n但所有截圖都冇keep<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近一隻 萌獸學園<br />\n一封頂已棄驚<br />\n<br />\n新olg根本唔耐玩<br />\n好想玩返d舊驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7665f27ac5e90aa5af1e0206d7f74ddabca0afb0","tid":407153,"uid":1818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:24:46.000Z","msg":"睇黎樓主應該未18歲"},{"pid":"b07df62b6fd6673d97689b59b0dd17c0fd936fc6","tid":407153,"uid":38539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img s